 ('1', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '1', NULL, '{\"typeId\":\"1\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Homepage\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1449342747,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":[]}', '2015-12-05 19:12:27', '2015-12-05 19:12:27', '186ac019-db08-4ee7-a373-6d86101f0c7f'),
 ('2', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '2', NULL, '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Welcome to Craft.jimchristie.me!\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1449342747,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":\"1\",\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>It\\u2019s true, this site doesn\\u2019t have a whole lot of content yet, but don\\u2019t worry. Our web developers have just installed the CMS, and they\\u2019re setting things up for the content editors this very moment. Soon Craft.jimchristie.me will be an oasis of fresh perspectives, sharp analyses, and astute opinions that will keep you coming back again and again.<\\/p>\"}}', '2015-12-05 19:12:27', '2015-12-05 19:12:27', '256f98f7-6404-4f7b-871f-2841c1043bb5'),
 ('15', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"1\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Random Triangles\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1453171596,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":[]}', '2016-07-06 23:56:48', '2016-07-06 23:56:48', '1065fb5d-a565-4c7d-b3f0-b0adfee7d97d'),
 ('16', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '4', '', '{\"typeId\":\"1\",\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Hello\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1453171596,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>I\'m Jim Christie. I\'m a web devoloper, an agile coach, a cyclist, and sometimes, an artist. As anyone who works on the internet should, I love cats.<\\/p><p>I&nbsp;have over five years of web development experience. I lean strongly toward back end functionality of websites. I can do design, but I don\'t love it and, consequently, I\'m not the best at it.<\\/p><p>I\'ve become a strong supporter of agile methodologies.<\\/p>\",\"2\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-07 00:22:12', '2016-07-07 00:22:12', 'd77a6e52-9220-4969-ac13-e06b130e6ca0'),
 ('17', '17', '5', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"7\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Untitled\",\"slug\":\"untitled\",\"postDate\":1470706910,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"<p>This was a project in a painting class in college. The assignment was to create a painting by pouring paint on the canvas. This was the second iteration of this assignment. The first was criticized by the professor as being too layered. My professor didn\'t like that he cold tell the order that the paint was poured onto the canvas, though I&nbsp;disagreed. However, in the interest of getting a good grade, I&nbsp;pushed my painting as far from that criticism as I&nbsp;could. This was the result, which I&nbsp;have been incredibly pleased with.<\\/p>\",\"5\":\"<p>Acrylic on canvas.<\\/p><p>Applied by mixing paint with water and pouring it onto the canvas. I&nbsp;then manipulated the canvas to force the paint to flow in different directions.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-08-09 01:41:51', '2016-08-09 01:41:51', '01ca564a-27d2-41dc-8879-a091d71dcb0e'),
 ('18', '17', '5', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"7\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Untitled\",\"slug\":\"untitled\",\"postDate\":1470706860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"<p>This was a project in a painting class in college. The assignment was to create a painting by pouring paint on the canvas. This was the second iteration of this assignment. The first was criticized by the professor as being too layered. My professor didn\'t like that he cold tell the order that the paint was poured onto the canvas, though I&nbsp;disagreed. However, in the interest of getting a good grade, I&nbsp;pushed my painting as far from that criticism as I&nbsp;could. This was the result, which I&nbsp;have been incredibly pleased with.<\\/p>\",\"7\":[\"18\"],\"5\":\"<p>Acrylic on canvas.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Applied by mixing paint with water and pouring it onto the canvas. I&nbsp;then manipulated the canvas to force the paint to flow in different directions.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-08-09 01:55:42', '2016-08-09 01:55:42', '87cf34fc-d415-420d-bb23-c261b33de4a3'),
 ('19', '17', '5', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"7\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Untitled\",\"slug\":\"untitled\",\"postDate\":1470706860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"<p>This was a project in a painting class in college. The assignment was to create a painting by pouring paint on the canvas. This was the second iteration of this assignment. The first was criticized by the professor as being too layered. My professor didn\'t like that he cold tell the order that the paint was poured onto the canvas, though I&nbsp;disagreed. However, in the interest of getting a good grade, I&nbsp;pushed my painting as far from that criticism as I&nbsp;could. This was the result, which I&nbsp;have been incredibly pleased with.<\\/p>\",\"7\":[\"19\"],\"5\":\"<p>Acrylic on canvas.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Applied by mixing paint with water and pouring it onto the canvas. I&nbsp;then manipulated the canvas to force the paint to flow in different directions.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-08-09 02:07:55', '2016-08-09 02:07:55', 'b6bb904c-8d58-4af2-9489-a39e6229e9f6'),
 ('20', '21', '5', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"6\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Puella\",\"slug\":\"puella\",\"postDate\":1471485820,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"<p>This is one of my cats. She\'s the best. And the worst.<\\/p>\",\"7\":[\"20\"],\"5\":\"<p>Digital. Created with AutoDesk Sketchbook on a Samsung Note Pro.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-08-18 02:03:40', '2016-08-18 02:03:40', 'd99c5303-5550-45eb-a074-6496140b9ce2'),
 ('21', '23', '5', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"6\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Puer\",\"slug\":\"puer\",\"postDate\":1471488427,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"6\":\"<p>One of my cats.&nbsp;He loves having his armpits scratched.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"7\":[\"22\"],\"5\":\"<p>Digital. I&nbsp;experimented quite a bit with this one. I&nbsp;started out using Artflow on a Samsung Note 8.0, but finished it in AutoDesk SketchBook on a Samsung Note Pro.<\\/p>\",\"4\":\"\"}}', '2016-08-18 02:47:07', '2016-08-18 02:47:07', 'fe0d5a61-8ff5-429f-93c5-d57309c1666f'),
